column2: 1 for summary of analytical findings at the top; else 0.7 for summary at the bottom;  else 0.7 for factual findings presented but not summarized; else 0.7 for want of thoroughness; else 0.5 for dataset description or other summary;

column4: 1 for all clauses (SELECT, FROM, WHERE, GROUP BY, ORDER BY, and either LIMIT or TOP); else 0.9 for missing a TOP or LIMIT; else 0.8 for missing a GROUP BY; else 0.6 for missing GROUP BY and TOP/LIMIT); else 0.5 for missing GROUP BY, ORDER BY, and TOP/LIMIT
